    <item>
      <title>赦免亨特使拜登的遗产设想变得复杂</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/02/us/politics/biden-pardon-criticized-democrats.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登总统坚称自己不会赦免儿子的罪名，如今却面临批评。据拜登党内一些批评人士称，此举为唐纳德·特朗普重返总统职位铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/02/us/politics/biden-pardon-criticized-democrats.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 01:18:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登获广泛赦免 专家表示忧虑</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2024/12/02/us/politics/hunter-biden-pardon-president.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登总统给予全面赦免，以防止他的儿子因海外业务而受到特朗普政府的起诉。专家们援引了历史相似之处。]]></description>
